Description:
You arrive at the market, but instead of merchants, you find only guards and their prisoners.

The leader of the guards informs you that they have just suppressed a slave revolt here and that you may continue your pilgrimage to the altars, although the merchants won’t be returning anytime soon.

Among the chained people are crocomen, nagas, and lizardmen. These must be some of the prisoners the naga mentioned when you arrived through the portal. You notice that some of them are discreetly hiding the fact that they are free from their chains, seemingly preparing for an escape.
DescriptionAction: Will you continue your journey or help them?
